On 5/21/05 3:37 PM, "Dave" <brooksdj(-at-)earthlink.net> wrote:

> Anyone know a source for the exhaust studs for a T4 motor?

The early studs are 8x53mm. The laster ones are stepped 8x9x56mm.

http://www.belmetric.com/html/catalog12.htm

These studs are identical to the Genuine VW studs and they are from indeed
from Germany. Minimum order is 10 studs for the step stud.

IIRC they were $3.89/ea.

